Realism/Hardcore mode:
    Comes with many changes that make your survival significantly more miserable.
    For hardcore players only. Death becomes way more punishing!

    On death:
        - 30s respawn time
        - Drop significant amount of your money, by following:
            1. The dropped value is 10% of your money
            2. The value is powered to ^0.75
            3. Apply slight softcap if it's above 5k

    Minimal HUD (Health, ammo remaining for specific weapon only)

    Body health system:
        Head: Very vulnerable. 0HP -> Death.
        Torso: The core part of your body, has vital organs. 0HP -> Death.
        Arms: You hold your weapons with it. Lower HP -> Worse aim
        Legs: They are what you walk with. Lower HP -> Worse movement speed

    and more

